Class CK_SSL3_KEY_MAT_PARAMS

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.safenetinc.jcprov.params.CK_SSL3_KEY_MAT_PARAMS

  • public class CK_SSL3_KEY_MAT_PARAMS
extends java.lang.Object
    Parameter for the
    CKM.SSL3_KEY_AND_MAC_DERIVE
    mechanism.

    Further information is provided in the PKCS#11 standard and the Programmers Manual.
